cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.Distributed, cs.AI. 

The paper focuses on improving the training process of large-scale CNNs through parallelism in distributed computing environments. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also addresses issues related to data communication, synchronization, and workload balance, which are relevant to cs.Distributed. Finally, the paper proposes strategies for task decomposition and scheduling, which are related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
